# Cost

You don't need a hard drive for Webconverger.

Koolu thin client: 179 (+30EUR shipping) from _info AT koolu.nl_ including vat
compared to the [Linutop's
280EUR](http://www.linutop.com/shop/product_info.php?products_id=28)

# Hands on

Phil Hands and Luke Leighton have done some [Koolu optimised packages.](http://ftp.hands.com/hands-deb/pool/koolu/)

## Still need to try

If you want to give is a try, boot any standard Etch install media, and at
the boot prompt, type:

    auto url=hands.com classes=koolu
